Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:43.33,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}无所指望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:47.98,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:51.96,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:55.50,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}有所准备
